Compare current and expected packages under .libPaths.

Source: R/base.R
lib_validate.Rd

Checking the healthy of the libarary.

lib_validate(lib.loc = NULL, fields = c("Depends", "Imports", "LinkingTo"))

Arguments

lib.loc

character. Default: NULL
fields

character vector with possible values c("Depends", "Imports", "LinkingTo", "Suggests"). Default: c("Depends", "Imports", "LinkingTo")

Value

data.frame with 3 columns Package Version.expected.min Version.have. "" means newest version.

Note

Version.expected.min column not count packages which are not a dependency for any package, so could not be find in DESCRIPTION files.

Examples

lib_validate()
